delete.description:
Remove a custom volume from the application. Only application volumes can be deleted;
service volumes are managed through the services API. Deleting a volume marks the
application as needing deployment.

get.description:
Returns aggregated /24 IP ranges for all Kubernetes nodes, grouped by region.
This endpoint is useful for clients who need to whitelist Ploi Cloud IP addresses
in their external services or firewalls.

## Response Format

```json
{
  "regions": {
    "ams1": [
      "185.52.172.0/24",
      "185.52.173.0/24"
    ]
  }
}
```
